            <i class="fas fa-search fa-3x"></i>
            <h3>Smart Search</h3>
            <p>Find exactly what you need with powerful filters by subject, grade level, and content type.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt fa-3x"></i>
